<materialsCitation id="74FC3CA3FF906A2FF77491B8173DB3AE" ID-GBIF-Occurrence="3783319428" latitude="32.7" longitude="21.583334" pageId="107" pageNumber="865">
“Central part of the Wadi Al Kuf (Jabal Akhdar Mts), ca. 
<quantity id="036C9B1BFF906A2FF6869E5D17C3B317" box="[2426,2499,2052,2085]" metricMagnitude="3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="8.0" pageId="107" pageNumber="865" unit="km" value="8.0">8 km</quantity>
